<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erreur serveur - GeoImpact Tech</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Raleway:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .error-page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        }
        
        .error-content {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .error-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .error-text {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn-light {
            background-color: white;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .btn-light:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .btn-outline-light {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 2px solid white;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-outline-light:hover {
            background-color: white;
            color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-page">
        <div class="error-content">
            <div class="error-code">500</div>
            <h1 class="error-title">Erreur interne du serveur</h1>
            <p class="error-text">Une erreur technique s'est produite. Notre équipe a été notifiée et travaille à résoudre le problème.</p>
            <div class="error-actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-light">
                    <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Retour à l'accueil
                </a>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-light">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Signaler le problème
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>